      <title>钱学森卸任后，瑞银任命瑞信资深人士胡锦涛为中国区总裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ubs-names-credit-suisse-veteran-hu-china-head-as-qian-steps-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团 (UBS Group AG) 任命瑞士信贷资深人士胡燕妮 (Janice Hu) 为中国区新任总裁，接替在中国工作九年多后决定辞职的钱学森 (Eugene Qian)。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ubs-names-credit-suisse-veteran-hu-china-head-as-qian-steps-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:41:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国发现欧盟白兰地存在倾销但暂时不征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/china-finds-dumping-of-eu-brandy-but-withholds-tariff-for-now</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，初步调查中发现欧洲白兰地制造商倾销的证据，但没有征收关税，这表明北京方面希望与欧盟进行谈判，处理从电动汽车到农业等各种贸易问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/china-finds-dumping-of-eu-brandy-but-withholds-tariff-for-now</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:28:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>董事会考虑发行红股计划，信实股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ambani-s-reliance-to-consider-one-on-one-bonus-share-issue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[信实工业有限公司 (Reliance Industries Ltd.) 表示，将考虑发行红股——这是该公司七年来的首次——其亿万富翁董事长穆克什·安巴尼 (Mukesh Ambani) 希望在继续向面向消费者的业务多元化发展的同时，回报股东。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ambani-s-reliance-to-consider-one-on-one-bonus-share-issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:26:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金属价格疲软引发资产减记，Implats 亏损</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/implats-posts-loss-as-weak-metal-prices-trigger-asset-writedowns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于金属价格暴跌导致这家南非矿业公司减记了资产价值，英帕拉铂金控股有限公司 (Impala Platinum Holdings Ltd.) 公布了财年的亏损。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/implats-posts-loss-as-weak-metal-prices-trigger-asset-writedowns</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:23:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙通胀率处于一年低位，欧洲央行将降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/spanish-inflation-cools-to-one-year-low-as-ecb-set-to-cut-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙通胀率降至一年来最低水平——欧元区通胀率可能也将出现回落，这使得欧洲央行得以继续降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/spanish-inflation-cools-to-one-year-low-as-ecb-set-to-cut-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国表示暂时不会征收关税，保乐力加股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pernod-says-us-china-sales-will-remain-soft-this-quarter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，尽管发现倾销证据，但暂时不会对欧盟白兰地征收临时关税。此后，保乐力加集团 (Pernod Ricard SA) 的股价与其他欧洲烈酒制造商一起上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/pernod-says-us-china-sales-will-remain-soft-this-quarter</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 05:27:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国电动汽车需求暴跌，欧洲汽车销售陷入停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/european-car-sales-stagnate-as-ev-demand-plummets-in-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲 7 月份汽车销量基本持平，因为该地区最大的汽车市场德国对电动汽车的需求进一步减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/european-car-sales-stagnate-as-ev-demand-plummets-in-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>铝供需平衡不佳导致基本金属价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/aluminum-leads-base-metals-down-on-dim-supply-and-demand-balance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中国需求复苏力度的担忧挥之不去，且供应仍然充足，铝价延续从两个月高点回落的势头。其他工业金属价格也出现下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/aluminum-leads-base-metals-down-on-dim-supply-and-demand-balance</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 02:39:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者权衡英伟达的预测，美国股指期货缩减跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/us-stock-futures-drop-as-nvidia-forecast-dims-ai-rally-s-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在英伟达公司发布好坏参半的盈利报告后，投资者对人工智能的前景进行了评估，美国股指期货收复早盘跌幅并转为持平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/us-stock-futures-drop-as-nvidia-forecast-dims-ai-rally-s-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 23:52:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利率焦点回归，英伟达股价持稳：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，全球股市趋稳，试图从英伟达公司令人失望的销售预测中恢复过来，因为交易员将注意力转向了降息的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 22:58:31 GMT</pubDate>
